OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foccasionally heavy and thundery rain,
OL,7,Frisk of hail and torrential downpours
OL,8,Fin south, this evening. The rain
OL,9,Fclears southeast overnight with some
OL,10,Fclear spells developing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA largely dry and bright
OL,13,Fmorning with some sunny spells but
OL,14,Fcloud increases from the south towards
OL,15,Fmidday. Outbreaks of occasionally
OL,16,Fheavy rain spreads erratically north
OL,17,Fthrough the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
