OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FBright
OL,6,Fstart Saturday with some sunny spells
OL,7,Fbut occasionally heavy rain spreads
OL,8,Feast in afternoon. Sunday and Monday
OL,9,Fsee sunny spells and showers with
OL,10,Ffresh southwesterly winds.
